# --- OpenSSL in Debian 12 (bookworm) base ---
# Packages: libssl3t64, openssl, openssl-provider-legacy (all from python:3.12.13-slim).
# Accepted 2026-04-21, review by 2026-05-21.
# These will clear when python:3.12.x-slim rebuilds against an updated bookworm-security
# mirror, or when Dependabot raises a python base-image bump (A3 docker ecosystem).
# Plan 064 D11 explicitly accepts live OS-package feed drift as residual risk monitored here.
CVE-2026-28390
CVE-2026-28388
CVE-2026-28389
CVE-2026-31789
CVE-2026-31790
