# --- pip 25.0.1 bundled with python:3.12.13-slim ---
# Accepted 2026-04-21, review by 2026-05-21.
# pip version ships with the Python base image. Fix lands when the Python maintainers
# roll a new patch image that bundles a newer pip. We deliberately do NOT run
# `pip install --upgrade pip` in the Dockerfile — that would pull whatever pip is
# latest at build time, weakening reproducibility, and is out of scope for Plan 064 D11.
CVE-2025-8869
CVE-2026-1703
